# Changelog

## v0.3.0 (2026-03-22)

### Enhancements

- [Config] New configuration schema — `locations` replace `rules`, `proxies` map for named upstream definitions, `defaults` for fallback behavior
- [Config] Named proxy definitions — define a proxy once, reference it by name from multiple locations
- [Config] Per-location `no_proxy` list — bypass proxy for specific destinations within a location; supports exact IP, CIDR, exact domain, `.domain` suffix match, and `*` wildcard
- [Config] `defaults.no_proxy` — additional always-direct destinations on top of the hardcoded `localhost`, `127.0.0.1`, `::1`
- [Config] Location matchers — OR logic within each array (`ssids`, `ips`, `domains`), AND logic across arrays
- [Config] Validation on startup — unknown proxy names, locations without matchers, invalid URLs all abort with a clear error
- [Config] Legacy format detection — clear error message with link to documentation when old `upstream`/`rules` format is detected
- [Router] `Decide()` now returns a `Decision` with resolved proxy URL, domain, DNS servers, and effective no_proxy list
- [Router] Always-no-proxy enforcement — `localhost`, `127.0.0.1`, `::1` are hardcoded and cannot be proxied regardless of config

### Bug fixes

- [Router] Fix CIDR matching for IP-based no_proxy entries

---

## v0.2.0 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [Proxy] Add `User-Agent` and `Proxy-Connection: Keep-Alive` headers to upstream CONNECT requests, matching real client behavior
- [Proxy] Add per-rule `dns` field — custom DNS servers used only for connections matching that rule, without touching system DNS settings
- [Proxy] Add automatic auth scheme negotiation via `proxyplease` — transparently handles Basic, NTLM, and Negotiate per-connection by inspecting `Proxy-Authenticate` on 407 responses
- [Config] Add `upstream_domain` field for Active Directory NTLM auth — keeps the upstream URL clean and parseable
- [Router] Log collapsed to single line per request — host shown only on rule match

### Bug fixes

- [Proxy] Fix recurring 407 Proxy Authentication Required after ~45 minutes — upstream switches from Basic to Negotiate on session expiry, now handled transparently
- [Proxy] Fix hang on CONNECT when upstream requires NTLM and domain is not provided
- [Proxy] Fix upstream URL parsing failure with `domain\user` or `domain/user` format in credentials
- [Proxy] Fix 407 authentication failures caused by missing `Proxy-Connection: Keep-Alive` header in CONNECT tunnel

---

## v0.1.5 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [Proxy] Add per-rule `dns` field — custom DNS servers used only for connections matching that rule, without touching system DNS settings
- [Proxy] Add comprehensive logging to all proxy error paths — 502 failures now include the exact reason
- [Config] Introduce `Decision` type returned by `Decide()`, carrying both action and DNS servers
- [Router] Add deduplicating logger — repeated identical entries are suppressed and summarized every 100 occurrences
- [Network] Add 250ms debounce and same-value guard to `networkDidChange` to coalesce rapid network events
- [Network] Move SSID cache seeding from `init()` to `StartNetworkListener()` — binary startup is now side-effect free for subcommands like `completion`, `version`, `help`
- [CLI] Add `unknown command` error for unrecognized subcommands instead of silently falling back to `run`
- [CLI] Redact upstream proxy password in logs using `url.Redacted()`

### Bug fixes

- [Proxy] Fix 502 errors caused by upstream proxy hostname DNS resolution failures on network switch
- [Network] Fix SSID change event firing twice per network transition due to duplicate `SCDynamicStore` key registration
- [Completion] Fix `completion bash` exiting with code 1 during Homebrew install due to `init()` side effects

---

## v0.1.4 (2026-03-19)

### Enhancements

- [CI] Package darwin-arm64 binary as `.tar.gz` archive instead of bare binary
- [CI] Update release asset and Homebrew formula URL to use archive

### Bug fixes

- [Formula] Fix Homebrew install failure caused by bare binary URL — Homebrew requires an archive format

---

## v0.1.3 (2026-03-18)

### Enhancements

- [Formula] Streamline shell completion generation and config file creation in Homebrew formula
- [Network] Improve network listener initialization — `SCDynamicStore` setup is now deferred to `StartNetworkListener()`

### Bug fixes

- [CI] Fix Homebrew tap push authentication using explicit token URL in `git push`

---

## v0.1.2 (2026-03-18)

### Bug fixes

